snippet.title: doxxed.
snippet.description:
This is the sad story of when the person who is suppose to be catching predators, turns into a predator. 

Enjoy

Also if you or a loved one has experienced being doxxed, please check this website out for information on removing your private information online. 

https://inteltechniques.com/workbook.html

We are always watching & recording.
